    <date day="17" month="April" year="2013"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>This document defines a new option for the Dynamic Host Configuration
   Protocol for IPv4 and IPv6.  This option can be used by the DHCP
   server to carry the VLAN identifier to the DHCP client to distinguish
   different connections in the access network.</t>
    </abstract>
  </front>
